OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fpersist across north and west Scotland
OL,7,Fovernight. Largely dry elsewhere with
OL,8,Flong clear spells. Cloud increasing
OL,9,Facross the south and west later.
OL,10,FColder than recent nights, with a risk
OL,11,Fof a grass frost in some prone rural
OL,12,Fspots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FWintry showers affect northern
OL,15,FScotland initially. Elsewhere, a cold
OL,16,Fstart in the sunshine. Heavy rain and
OL,17,Fstrong winds will spread from Northern
OL,18,FIreland into the western areas late.
OL,19,FCoastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
